Author: David Schmetterling

Program functionalities:

1) Check the rotate box to rotate the figure
	2) if the rotate box is checked, click anywhere on the canvase to reverse the rotation
3) Pressing 'r' will change the color to red
4) Pressing 'b' will change the color to blue
5) Pressing 'g' will change the color to green
6) Pressing '+' will increase the number of triangles (you need to hold shift)
7) Pressing '-' will decrease the number of triangles
8) Pressing 'k' will increase the size of the polygon by increasing the radius
9) Pressing 'm' will decrease the size of the polygon by decreasing the radius
10) Dragging on the speed slider will increase the speed of rotation when rotation is enabled